ossible\nimplications of given model are also discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 25 Mar 2004 11:52:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 29 Mar 2004 10:00:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
